    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of naturally aspirated precision. At its heart is the S54B32 power plant, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and proactive rod bearing replacement, addressing the platform's critical mechanical focal points. Power is delivered via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of clear-coat failure or panel misalignment, while the suspension remains tight with OEM bushings and dampers. This is a turn-key, mechanically sorted masterpiece for the purist seeking uncompromised longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
