    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2019 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic over Black leather. This vehicle is the definition of showroom quality, having been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory finish with no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin still carries that new-car aroma; the leather bolsters are firm with zero signs of wear, and the buttons retain their crisp, tactile feedback. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, with a complete service history exclusively through Porsche authorized centers. It sits on a set of fresh Michelin Pilot Sport tires with 95% tread remaining. This is a collector-grade example that has been pampered by a single enthusiast owner. Includes both keys, original window sticker, and all service receipts. No accidents, no stories, just perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
